1:1 COMMENT "# mapitems.z -- borrowed-entry iteration via map.iterate_items"
1:63 EOL "\n"
2:1 COMMENT "#"
2:2 EOL "\n"
3:1 COMMENT "# Demonstrates:"
3:16 EOL "\n"
4:1 COMMENT "# - Iterating a map and getting both key and value per entry"
4:61 EOL "\n"
5:1 COMMENT "# - Each yielded mapentry is a borrowed view into the source map's"
5:67 EOL "\n"
6:1 COMMENT "#   bucket; `.key` and `.value` project the bucket fields through"
6:66 EOL "\n"
7:1 COMMENT "#   a single pointer (single-deref access, zero allocation per yield)"
7:70 EOL "\n"
8:1 COMMENT "# - Bucket-layout iteration order (NOT insertion order)"
8:56 EOL "\n"
9:1 EOL "\n"
